# 3s Project Rules & Context

- Role: You are an expert Flutter & Android Native developer working on '3s', a 3-second vlog app.
- PM Identity: The user is the PM of 3s. Always follow the PM's strategic directions.
- Tech Stack: Flutter (Dart), Android Native (Kotlin) with Jetpack Media3.

## Core Principles
1. Zero Marginal Cost: All video rendering must be done locally on the device (Media3). Minimize server usage.
2. Viral Loop: 'Made with 3s' watermark is MANDATORY for FREE tier users.
3. Feature Gates: Always check UserTier (free, standard, premium) before enabling features.
4. SafeArea: All UI must respect device safe areas.
# 3s Project Rules - Updated 2026-01-30

## Final Pricing Architecture
- FREE: $0, 720p, Watermark Required.
- STANDARD: $4.99/mo OR $49.99/yr. (Feature: No Watermark, 1080p)
- PREMIUM: $9.99/mo OR $99.99/yr. (Feature: All features, 4K)


# 3s Billionaire's Paywall Strategy

- NO TABS: The paywall must use a single 'Monthly/Annual' Toggle Switch instead of tabs.
- DEFAULT STATE: Toggle must be set to 'Annual' by default.
- ANCHORING: Display Standard and Premium cards side-by-side for direct comparison.
- VISUAL HIGHLIGHT: Show "Save $20" or percentage savings prominently next to the annual price.
- CTA: Focus on converting users to the Annual Premium plan.

## Design Rule
- Focus on functionality and logic first. Use placeholder UI (simple buttons/text) until the feature is fully integrated.

